What matters most is to take a step. So grab a coffee and #MakeYourMove. 

We shot this video under the Gariahat flyover where several locals stop by for a game of chess. Gariahat is also where we have Roastery Coffee House in Kolkata. It is always fascinating to see this spot where time seems to run a different pace as compared to the hustle bustle around it.

#InstaPour  #RoasteryCoffeeHouse #Coffee #specialtycoffee #growninindia #madeinindia #brew #brewcoffee #lovetobrewcoffee

Our letter of love to Lucknow. 

As we gear up to give you the warmest welcome, we can’t help but share that we feel overwhelmingly fortunate to call Lucknow our new home. It was love at first sight when we first set foot, and as the cafe came into life, the love grew in leaps and bounds. We cannot wait to open our doors to you, your friends, family and loved ones. Come on over and experience Indian specialty coffee in an 8000 square feet space designed to be your home away from home.

#lucknowtimes #lucknowcity #lucknow #specialitycoffeeroasters #indiancoffee #cityofnawabs #roasterycoffeehouse #roasterylucknow #coffee #cafe #indiancoffee #incredibleindia #CoffeeShots #lucknowdiaries #lucknowexplorer

Roastery Coffee House welcomes you to explore the art of roasting coffee and to create your own roast profile just like @chefshaunkenworthy. 
Founder and owner, @nishant.roastery was ecstatic to share the joys of roasting with Shaun. Both spoke at length about their love for flavours and the city of Kolkata as they roasted a fresh batch of beans to match Shaun’s preferences in coffee strength, acidity and tasting notes.

Nothing makes us happier than sharing our love for coffee. The next time you are at Roastery, remember to fill up the form and tell us how you like your coffee. Our team will create a roast that matches your palate.

Did you know, we set up a roasting unit in our Kolkata outlet this year to meet the growing demands for specialty coffee in Eastern India — it has increased three times since the year we opened!

Roastery Coffee feat. @chefshaunkenworthy 

We were delighted to have celebrity chef, Mr Shaun Kenworthy drop by Roastery Coffee House, Kolkata to create his own roast profile. Owner and Founder, Nishant Sinha took him through the process as they explored the beautiful art of roasting coffee beans.

✨ Two worlds. One sip.
There’s something beautiful about pairing litchi’s sweetness with espresso’s depth. Two layers, two flavors — and with one stir, they blend into a drink that surprises and delights.

This is the kind of coffee you didn’t know you needed — light, refreshing, and just a little playful.

Perfect for slow brunches, sweet moments, or whenever you feel like trying something new.

Roastery Coffee House - Kokapet - Hyderabad

Step into a world where timeless architecture meets the aroma of freshly brewed coffee. Nestled amidst lush greenery and bathed in natural light, project blends serene ambiance with artisanal flavors.

From the warm, arched windows to the signature terracotta-and-white façade, every corner is crafted for comfort and conversation. 

Client: @roasterycoffeehouseindia 
📸-: @taranggoyal_

✨ Meet Litchi and Coffee at Roastery

Litchi’s gentle sweetness meets the depth of espresso, two contrasting worlds blended into one beautiful drink.
The drink you didn’t know you needed.

A top seller and crowd favorite at Roastery Coffee House but one we’ve never spoken about until now.
Another gem we created after our trademarked Cranberry Coffee.

🍸 Why it’s special:
• The sweetness of litchi highlights the fruitiness of coffee.
• The espresso’s bittersweet character balances the drink perfectly.
• Comes with a bit of visual drama, two contrasting layers that invite you to stir and sip.

🌞 Best enjoyed:
• With a slow brunch
• Alongside your favorite cake
• Under the warm café light

📍 Where to find it:
Exclusively at Roastery Coffee House, @colocalchocolates , and @pscheese.cafe

latestPosts.caption:
Real People. 
Real Moments. 
Through Your Lens.

From refreshing greens to corners blushing under the golden gleams, this is Roastery
through your lens.

We caught some magical moments brewing in our spaces:

From looking for an escape and actually finding a beautiful one. Ft. @pushpansh_katara 
To reflecting on your day and getting lost in thought. Ft. @ginniez_ramble
From tasting a slice of the blue skies. Ft. @mugswithmama
To crinkly fries and warm crinkly smiles. Ft. @lucknowfoodbites
From widening smiles and widening love from corner to corner. Ft. @avneesh_ironside
To admiring the palace’s grandeur through a glass of simple pleasures. Ft. @desiaudrey
From sipping the sun in a shining cup of coffee. Ft. @shabaazshaaz
To letting us taste a piece of joy on your birthday. Ft @singh.muskan20 

Thank you for seeing Roastery the way we feel it.
Your moments make this place special.
Here’s to many more, together.
